  {
    "start": 23.16,
    "end": 26.76,
    "en": "in which an orange fish is separated from his father.",
    "ko": "주황색 물고기가 아빠와 헤어지는 영화야."
  },
  {
    "start": 27.06,
    "end": 28.32,
